This is the root for the sphinx documentation for pypsyexp. 

==============================
=== Building documentation === 
==============================

- To build html documentation, at the shell type:

make html # generates an html website in build/html


- To build latex documentation, type:

make latex  # generates latex files in build/latex
cd build/latex
make  # runs pdflatex on latex files

=======================
=== Important files ===
=======================

Site files are in ReST format in the root of source, e.g. index.rst

Sphinx configuration is done in source/conf.py

The html template used is in source/_templates

The css template used, as well as images that are embedded in the website, can
be found in source/_static.

